  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd1\u0db1\u0dca - \u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddc\u0dca\u0daf \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0da7\u0dd3 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0da7:\u0d85\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Van - three-wheeler collision, two dead: one in hospital",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to Dodangoda Police, two people have died and another person has been seriously injured in a head-on collision between a van and a three-wheeler in Malabada area of \u200b\u200bDodangoda.",
        "The police said that the three-wheeler was going towards Kalutara from Matugama after getting fuel from Yadola petrol station, and the van was going towards Matugama from Kalutara.",
        "The police said that the two people who were traveling behind the three-wheeler died in the accident and they were residents of Sapugahawatta area in Dodangoda.",
        "It is also said that the condition of the three-wheeler driver who has been taken to the hospital is quite serious."
      ],
